<p>The Industrial Works of Bay City, Michigan was a firm which manufactured locomotive cranes.</p>
</bioghist>


<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The record group includes a history, financial material, and correspondence. Most of the correspondence concerning merger with McMyler-Interstate Co. of Cleveland, Ohio.</p>
</scopecontent>

